Package: carbon
Title: Get the CO2 ppm Value Closest to a Given Date
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Valentin",
           family = "Lucey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "valentin.lucet@gmail.com")
Description: Retrieves weekly CO2 ppm from the Mauna Loa observatory data hub,
    and provides a simple function that retrieves the ppm value closest to a
    given date.
